'''Mikish''' was the most infamous [[platform city]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Cularin/Legends|Cularin]]. It was also the seat of [[Restimar Mining Corporation]], from which its [[Mining/Legends|mining]] operations on [[Tilnes]] were run.<ref name="LFC">''[[Living Force Campaign Guide]]''</ref>

Many of Mikish's [[Law enforcement agency/Legends|police officers]] were corrupt, and they all had outside jobs of one kind or another. The [[City/Legends|city]] also had looser weapons ordinances than the other platform cities.<ref name="LFC" />

Mikish was the center of [[Nirama]]'s criminal enterprises on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]]. [[Riboga]] the [[Hutt/Legends|Hutt]] used to have a mansion there, and Nirama operated from that mansion when he was on Cularin,<ref name="LFC" /> as when he met with the people responsible of the [[Death/Legends|death]] of one of his [[Pilot/Legends|pilots]] in [[32 BBY/Legends|32 BBY]]<ref name="POB">{{LivingForce|The Price of Business}}</ref>.

